ld, parent);\n                Object ancestor = findAncestorWithClass.invoke(null, child, tagClass);\n\n                assertThat(ancestor).isSameAs(parent);\n            }\n        } catch (Error error) {\n            if (!NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(error)) {\n                throw error;\n            }\n        }\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void managesTagStateAndScopedValues() {\n","newText":"        Tag invalidAncestorType = TagSupport.findAncestorWithClass(child, Object.class);\n        Tag nearestTagAncestor = TagSupport.findAncestorWithClass(child, Tag.class);\n        Tag nearestConcreteAncestor = TagSupport.findAncestorWithClass(child, parent.getClass());\n        Tag missingAncestor = TagSupport.findAncestorWithClass(child, BodyTag.class);\n\n        assertThat(invalidAncestorType).isNull();\n        assertThat(nearestTagAncestor).isSameAs(parent);\n        assertThat(nearestConcreteAncestor).isSameAs(parent);\n        assertThat(missingAncestor).isNull();\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    void managesTagStateAndScopedValues() {\n"},{"oldText":"\n    private static final class ChildFirstJspClassLoader extends URLClassLoader {\n        private ChildFirstJspClassLoader(URL libraryUrl) {\n            super(new URL[] {libraryUrl}, TagSupportTest.class.getClassLoader());\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        protected synchronized Class<?> loadClass(String name, boolean resolve)\n                throws ClassNotFoundException {\n            if (name.startsWith(\"javax.servlet.jsp.\")) {\n                Class<?> loadedClass = findLoadedClass(name);\n                if (loadedClass == null) {\n                    try {\n                        loadedClass = findClass(name);\n                    } catch (ClassNotFoundException ignored) {\n                        loadedClass = super.loadClass(name, false);\n                    }\n                }\n                if (resolve) {\n                    resolveClass(loadedClass);\n                }\n         